In re WEST 163d ST. IN CITY OF NEW YORK. In the matter of the City of New York, for West 163d Street. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division. First Department. June 25, 1909.)

With this case has been consolidated in this court cases bearing titles as follows: In re West 162d St. in the City of New York; In re West 161st St. in the City of New York; and In re West 160th St. in the City of New York.

No opinions. Motions to dismiss appeals granted, with $10 costs. Orders filed.
